44c56c81c30ba468","tid":782774,"uid":606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T05:15:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95ee731a12c7551d63a4987df719d3c801b4bbcd","tid":782774,"uid":26862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T05:21:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90ca1b4ac6ad638c456ea5d75fbdea57b8640874","tid":782774,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T05:28:57.000Z","msg":"　聲優事務所青二製作於今（17）日證實，曾演出動畫《精靈寶可夢》大木博士、旁白，以及《JOJO 的奇妙冒險 星塵鬥士》喬瑟夫 &middot; 喬斯達等知名角色的聲優石塚運昇在 13 日因為食道癌過世，享年 68 歳。<br />\n<br />\n石塚以《精靈寶可夢》大木博士、《灌籃高手》田岡教練（陵南）等角色為人所知，此外經常演出像《頭文字 D》的藤原文太等成熟男性角色，在鄉里大輔去世後也接演了像是《七龍珠》撒旦等角色。由於《精靈寶可夢》的長紅，曾多次擔任劇場版宣傳的嘉賓，也曾參與歌曲演唱。<br />\n <br />\n　　根據所屬事務所的聲明，告別式將僅由親屬舉行家族葬禮，至於是否舉辦追思會，則會根據遺族的意願來決定，將於日後再對外報告。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/6/166976.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgnn.gamer.com.tw%2F6%2F166976.html&d=11haNinqpFo5c%2BYx51pCKwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=1d01123a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/6/166976.html</a>"},{"pid":"d5de08012ff84555401f7ede96bb5eaad0f4f7c1","tid":782774,"uid":30235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T05:29:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49b1d4d62df1b5120af2fc88e57114367e085ace","tid":782774,"uid":131625,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T05:31:30.000Z","msg":"最深刻都係jojo同兼一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"